5 sources of drinking water.
6 (ii) All contamination at the site has been remediated.
7 (iii) The soil at the site has been stabilized and
8 rehabilitated.
9 (iv) The ecosystem has been restored.
10 (6) Payment under an instrument required by subsection (5)
11 does not relieve the operator from any other legal requirements.
12 Assets under the instrument revert to the operator's control, at
